column5: Im looking for a MG service centre near Milton. Only place I could find on the web was Aikmans. Anything closer?  Also I think I missed the warranty by 3 months:(. I guess I should have sent it in last fall when it failed.
dont think youll find anything closers then Aikmans. its only half hr from milton?
Yeah, I finally got the MG site to work on my phone and Aikmans is the closest. Thanks Boss
